OL,3,C'No evidence' found over alleged rape
OL,4,Cwhich sparked Epsom protests, police
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FDetectives have said they are yet to
OL,8,Ffind evidence that an alleged rape
OL,9,Foutside a church took place as
OL,10,Freported or that any immigrants or
OL,11,Fasylum seekers were involved.
OL,13,FSurrey Police previously received a
OL,14,Freport that a woman in her 20s had
OL,15,Fbeen followed and assaulted outside
OL,16,Fthe church in Ashley Road, Epsom,
OL,17,Fafter leaving Labyrinth Epsom
OL,18,Fnightclub on Saturday between 2am and
OL,19,F4am.
