OL,3,C'No evidence' found over alleged rape
OL,4,Cwhich sparked Epsom protests, police
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe force are yet to provide any
OL,8,Fdescriptions of suspects, which led to
OL,9,Fa large crowd of protesters gathering
OL,10,Fon Wednesday evening.
OL,12,FIn a statement issued on Friday, the
OL,13,Fforce said: "There has been much
OL,14,Fspeculation about the non-release of a
OL,15,Fdescription of any suspects,
OL,16,Fespecially regarding the ethnicity.
OL,18,F"No descriptions have been released as
OL,19,Fthe information about the incident and
OL,20,Fpotential suspects is so limited.
